# Deployment-specific verification tokens (each deploy generates its own).
# .indexnow-key = local note of the key filename.
# [0-9a-f]*.txt = the IndexNow key file, e.g. e5512bca….txt (keep it out of git).
# google*.html = Google Search Console verification file.
.indexnow-key
[0-9a-f]*.txt
google*.html

